</p>
<p>health care in the United States, a critical review&#8221;, <i>Social Science &amp; Medicine</i>, vol. 74, Iss. 6 (March 
2012), p. 824. 
</p>
<p> 82  PICUM, <i>Access to Health Care</i>, p. 45 (see footnote 76). 
